<item>
            <title>[SEC-1848] AbstractLdapAuthenticator must escape username</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1848</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AbstractLdapAuthenticator.getUserDns() must escape provided username before fomatting it into userDnFormat. It should use LdapEncoder.nameEncode().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
